g.text: Title: TANDY WP-2 128K RAM IC Card
The Small-TSOP (8x14) version of some parts (ex: CY62128ELL-55ZAXI)
use a pin numbering that doesn't match the sTSOP symbol above,
but all parts still have the same signals at the same physical pin locations.
The PCB is compatible with these parts, just disregard the pin numbers used in the datasheet.
Example compatible SRAM parts: TC551001 IS61C1024 IS62C1024 CY62128 CY7C109D AS6C1008 AS7C1024B R1LP0108E
